{"TopicId":187280,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"X-37B","CreatedByName":"Kerbal01","CreatedById":57322,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-07T14:20:42Z","PageNum":5,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"mikegarrison","CreatedById":137807,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-14T03:59:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223939921\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615667711\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210324\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ziggy Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Ziggy Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nX-37B- The irl, \u0022exposed materials to space and recorded the results\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wouldn\u0027t be surprised if they have a canister of mystery goo stashed away in their hold.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-22T21:19:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223939921\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615667711\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210324\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ziggy Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/13/2021 at 11:35 PM, Ziggy Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nX-37B- The irl, \u0022exposed materials to space and recorded the results\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s about the right hull diameter, too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mikegarrison","CreatedById":137807,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-05T23:56:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe are nearing 1 year for the current X-37B mission. Probably only about another year and a half to go....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T00:20:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEarlier, people speculated about space piracy / privateering / prize taking with this - and then speculated about how easy it is to prevent your spysat from getting snatched.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWouldn\u0027t it be easier to just pull up next to the offending spysat and just pop a can of glitter?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T01:01:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967122\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620258962\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137807\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mikegarrison\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, mikegarrison said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe are nearing 1 year for the current X-37B mission. Probably only about another year and a half to go....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nX-37B is pretty amazing... I was really surprised when they pulled out of that DARPA project to make that other spaceplane (name escapes me).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T04:52:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967130\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620260451\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEarlier, people speculated about space piracy / privateering / prize taking with this - and then speculated about how easy it is to prevent your spysat from getting snatched.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey should just negotiate and rent each other\u0027s spysat.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967155\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620262885\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nX-37B is pretty amazing... I was really surprised when they pulled out of that DARPA project to make that other spaceplane (name escapes me).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe success\u00A0stolen from DynaSoar.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T04:53:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967266\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620276723\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe success\u00A0stolen from DynaSoar.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDream Chaser, too. It was a good idea then, it\u0027s a good idea now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T04:58:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967268\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620276789\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDream Chaser, too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDream Chaser is not actually a success to the date. It\u0027s a success embryo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T05:24:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967271\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620277106\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDream Chaser is not actually a success to the date. It\u0027s a success embryo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is true.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nObX-37B content (for awesomeness):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022200506-F-XX000-0003.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022150.00\u0022 height=\u00221200\u0022 width=\u0022800\u0022 src=\u0022https://mk0spaceflightnoa02a.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/200506-F-XX000-0003.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T05:44:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967130\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620260451\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWouldn\u0027t it be easier to just pull up next to the offending spysat and just pop a can of glitter?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s considered a legitimate strategy. There are better materials than glitter, though, like Vual\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://thespacereview.com/article/3536/1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://thespacereview.com/article/3536/1\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T05:51:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620279878\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s considered a legitimate strategy. There are better materials than glitter, though, like Vual\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://thespacereview.com/article/3536/1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://thespacereview.com/article/3536/1\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn Soviet Russia even city buses were equipped with cloaking devices,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022videoPreview?id=12051809747\u0026amp;type=47\u0026amp;idx=\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022405\u0022 width=\u0022720\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.mycdn.me/videoPreview?id=12051809747\u0026amp;type=47\u0026amp;idx=30\u0026amp;tkn=5FT1c-te5pG33dGinF9N82AAd60\u0026amp;i=1\u0026amp;fn=external_8\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n***\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet all spysat owners\u00A0just add a common layer in Google Earth and save each other\u0027s money by providing it with pix.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-05-06T05:51:50Z\u0022 title=\u002205/06/2021 05:51  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EMay 6, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T14:32:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620279878\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s considered a legitimate strategy. There are better materials than glitter, though, like Vual\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://thespacereview.com/article/3536/1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://thespacereview.com/article/3536/1\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh - I love how whenever I come up with a brilliant idea some engineer already made it (and even a \u003Cem\u003Ebetter\u003C/em\u003E version) decades prior.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the read!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T05:12:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=\u0026amp;sl=ru\u0026amp;tl=en\u0026amp;u=https://www.rbc.ru/technology_and_media/22/05/2021/60a93f219a7947f0262cf81c\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://translate.google.com/translate?hl=\u0026amp;sl=ru\u0026amp;tl=en\u0026amp;u=https://www.rbc.ru/technology_and_media/22/05/2021/60a93f219a7947f0262cf81c\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDuring the \u0022New Knowledge\u0022 forum, the CEO of the main Russian AA-missiles manufacturer \u0022Almaz-Antey\u0022 stated that X-37 can be a nuclear weapon carrier.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe said, that there are already six of them (37s), some of them bigger, some of them smaller.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe said, that while officially they are made for scientific and spy purposes, but Russia understands that their capacity allows them to carry from 3 (for the smaller one) to 6 (for the bigger one) warheads.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe said, that by 2025 US are planning to put into orbit two more such crafts, and this is of course a serious challenge.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SOXBLOX","CreatedById":204106,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T05:43:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLOL, whatever. Like the X-37 can do inclination changes at will to hit [insert random Russian city here]. Has that guy even played KSP?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T06:03:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977310\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621748621\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204106\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SOXBLOX\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 minutes ago, SOXBLOX said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLOL, whatever. Like the X-37 can do inclination changes at will to hit [insert random Russian city here]. Has that guy even played KSP?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Almaz-Antey\u0022\u0027s S-500 is officially and anti-sat missile,\u00A0too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scotius","CreatedById":57622,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T07:15:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*eyeroll* Every satellite in orbit can be a potential nuke carrier. Every crewed spacecraft too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone is fearmongering hard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T07:21:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977329\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621754122\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257622\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Scotius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Scotius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*eyeroll* Every satellite in orbit can be a potential nuke carrier. Every crewed spacecraft too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone is fearmongering hard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977310\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621748621\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204106\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SOXBLOX\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, SOXBLOX said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLOL, whatever. Like the X-37 can do inclination changes at will to hit [insert random Russian city here]. Has that guy even played KSP?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne word: Vandenberg. Also, from what I\u0027ve heard the Shuttle could use its wings for aerodynamic plane change maneuvers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway, the people behind the study that justified Buran never recanted their opinion that the Shuttle was a bomber.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.thespacereview.com/article/3855/1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.thespacereview.com/article/3855/1\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.thespacereview.com/article/3873/1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.thespacereview.com/article/3873/1\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.thespacereview.com/article/3876/1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.thespacereview.com/article/3876/1\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis contributes to certain... \u0022alternative facts\u0022 circulating in the Russian defence community.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-05-23T07:24:41Z\u0022 title=\u002205/23/2021 07:24  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EMay 23, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by DDE\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T07:31:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile X-37 is obviously a carrier of some equipment to be exposed for long time in the space conditions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnlikely material samples, as too much efforts for just another set of plates.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDefinitely not a bomber, as why keep it in orbit and have just two of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnlikely a spy, as too puny, compared to real spysats.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill thinking, it exposes some deactivated nukes to see how they feel in real space for years.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThough, maybe something\u00A0electronic and emitting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA spaceplane - to secretly and safely return it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts maneuvering capability is\u00A0to cowardly take evasive actions, when a peaceful, civil, scientific Russian sputnik, equipped with geigers and magnetometers,\u00A0is suddenly going to pass by at close distance with absolutely no\u00A0intention to inspect its emission spectre.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SOXBLOX","CreatedById":204106,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T14:09:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977337\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621755098\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts maneuvering capability is\u00A0to cowardly take evasive actions, when a peaceful, civil, scientific Russian sputnik, equipped with geigers and magnetometers,\u00A0is suddenly going to pass by at close distance with absolutely no\u00A0intention to inspect its emission spectre.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll petition the government to send up a space-adapted Phalanx CIWS next launch!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977331\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621754461\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, from what I\u0027ve heard the Shuttle could use its wings for aerodynamic plane change maneuvers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIDK how it would do this. It would have to enter the atmosphere, and then return to orbit. I think...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-05-23T14:09:46Z\u0022 title=\u002205/23/2021 02:09  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EMay 23, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by SOXBLOX\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T16:35:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621778963\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204106\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SOXBLOX\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, SOXBLOX said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIDK how it would do this. It would have to enter the atmosphere, and then return to orbit. I think...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, not if it\u0027s attempting a single-orbit mission, which is very likely under wartime conditions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut since low orbit is in the exosphere, some (admittedly low-quality) slurces mentioned appreciable inclination effects from the Shuttle\u0027s wings even up there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621778963\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204106\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SOXBLOX\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, SOXBLOX said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll petition the government to send up a space-adapted Phalanx CIWS next launch!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022khau-phao-vu-tru-duy-nhat-the-gioi-la-ta\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002260.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://photo-cms-kienthuc.zadn.vn/zoomh/800/uploaded/ctvquansu/2021_02_17/tin_4/khau-phao-vu-tru-duy-nhat-the-gioi-la-tac-pham-cua-lien-xo-Hinh-13.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course, all of you are missing the bigger picture. Do you remember what the \u003Cem\u003Eprevious\u003C/em\u003E CEO of Almaz-Antei is at?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://asgardia.space/en/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://asgardia.space/en/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T16:57:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRelevant to our discussion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3135519450\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=https://mobile.twitter.com/KomissarWhipla/status/1396473699730169859\u0022 style=\u0022height:882px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nX-37B is labelled as \u0022Low-orbit and \u003Cstrong\u003Einter-media\u003C/strong\u003E spacecraft\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T17:51:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIS is, isn\u0027t it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222b6a6023c7e82de24c64a4af6b7d9425_cropped\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002272.80\u0022 height=\u0022728\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022 src=\u0022https://images11.popmeh.ru/upload/img_cache/2b6/2b6a6023c7e82de24c64a4af6b7d9425_cropped_1000x728.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T13:01:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977526\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621792298\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIS is, isn\u0027t it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EReveal hidden contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://images11.popmeh.ru/upload/img_cache/2b6/2b6a6023c7e82de24c64a4af6b7d9425_cropped_1000x728.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00222b6a6023c7e82de24c64a4af6b7d9425_cropped\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002272.80\u0022 height=\u0022728\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022 src=\u0022https://images11.popmeh.ru/upload/img_cache/2b6/2b6a6023c7e82de24c64a4af6b7d9425_cropped_1000x728.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe arc of history is long, but inevitably it bends towards \u003Cem\u003EWh40k\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022C4LJZk7uGYj1.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002281.00\u0022 height=\u0022678\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://rozetked.me/images/uploads/C4LJZk7uGYj1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-04T06:06:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223977329\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621754122\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257622\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Scotius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/23/2021 at 10:15 AM, Scotius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*eyeroll* Every satellite in orbit can be a potential nuke carrier. Every crewed spacecraft too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone is fearmongering hard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou know you dun goofed when even RT starts dunking on your scaremongering.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.rt.com/op-ed/525493-us-space-nukes-boeing/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.rt.com/op-ed/525493-us-space-nukes-boeing/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-04T07:36:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Buran-B Orbital Bomber\u0022 data-ratio=\u002299.61\u0022 width=\u0022765\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.globalsecurity.org/space/world/russia/images/buran-b-image02.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Buran-B Orbital Bomber\u0022 data-ratio=\u002257.22\u0022 width=\u0022720\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.globalsecurity.org/space/world/russia/images/buran-b-image01.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course, its not reliable, and that\u0027s not exactly\u00A0why the world military requires a 2 000 km crosswind maneuver from any spaceplane-looking thing, and not why HTV-2 performed a 2 000 km long hypersonic trip with S-maneuver.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HTV-2. \u0410\u043D\u0430\u0442\u043E\u043C\u0438\u044F \u0433\u0438\u043F\u0435\u0440\u0437\u0432\u0443\u043A\u0430 (\u0421\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043D\u0438\u0446\u0430 1) \u2014 \u002B \u041E\u0431\u0437\u043E\u0440\u043D\u044B\u0435 \u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442\u044C\u0438 \u2014 \u0424\u043E\u0440\u0443\u043C \u0441\u0430\u0439\u0442\u0430  \u00AB\u0412\u043E\u0435\u043D\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u043F\u0430\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0435\u0442\u00BB\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.00\u0022 width=\u0022800\u0022 src=\u0022http://forum.militaryparitet.com/extensions/hcs_image_uploader/uploads/290000/3500/293907/p1d1sqk0531oh518as181684p1mve2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThough, exactly X-37B of course unlikely could be a bomber/missile, due to its too aristocratic design.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n***\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoth USSRussia and Americanada/Canamerica are ~ 5 000 km wide. China as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, a 2 000 km crosswind aerodynamic maneuver on aerobraking means that a deorbited glider can reach most part of them without a need to pass exactly above.\u003Cbr\u003E\nObviously, its accuracy is much higher than accuracy of a bomb dropped from orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, the modern hypersonic trend is also exactly about this, too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut it\u0027s a question of 10..20 year perspective, when X-37B will be a relict derelict.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-06-04T07:45:52Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2021 07:45  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}